Finance/Shares/Log
==================

More than just an object keeping track of activity in the Finance::Shares
database and modelling suite, this also exports functions used by others in that
family.  Therefore, it is probably required by all Finance::Shares modules.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  File::Spec
  Date::Pcalc

